<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Our departments and services</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p>Castle Hill Hospital accommodates the Queen's Centre  for Oncology and Haematology, Cardiac and Elective Surgical facilities, the Medical Research Teaching and Day Surgery facilities and the ENT, Breast Surgery, and Plastic Surgery facility</p>
</div>
</div>
